{"tid":671404,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"做人老公好艱難","createTime":"2018-05-20T06:17:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-20T16:08:38.000Z","uid":4326,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"817334d55f91dc418e146b816351d7e3018fd024","tid":671404,"uid":4326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T06:17:35.000Z","msg":"結左婚一段時間<br />\n<br />\n老婆成日為小事嬲。大家觀點與角度問題<br />\n<br />\n只不過唔係佢諗住觀點出發。有時傾傾下語氣大左少少或者覺得講我唔明唔係起佢觀點就嬲<br />\n<br />\n其實好多時候我都就曬佢。只不過有時都想佢企起我觀點諗下<br />\n<br />\n一嬲就唔出聲。自己&quot;古&quot;埋拋鰓起度喊<br />\n<br />\n我好想解決問題。。但可惜佢一嬲就係咁<br />\n<br />\n同佢拍拖同結婚都無變過。。佢樣樣野都好好我都好愛佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 只可惜就係頂佢唔順依樣野<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n平時返工好大壓力。到左放工返到屋企又要見到佢咁。返工又比人鬧。放工又比老婆黑面<br />\n<br />\n可能係我唔識做人所以老婆事業兩失意<br />\n<br />\n其他人睇我好似好成功有份唔差嘅咁又有個咁好嘅老婆。。所以我都唔識點同班朋友講<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唉。。。做人真係做得好失敗"},{"pid":"69d30d3307d03008dc1d68fc02e2907c46981ee5","tid":671404,"uid":119900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T06:19:41.000Z","msg":"試下放左工返屋企唔出聲。會舒服啲"},{"pid":"946dd53d93547c9dbce575c1e39e739fab37c63f","tid":671404,"uid":138138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T06:20:49.000Z","msg":"硬食"},{"pid":"014d43624b56008ede2eae7b57b7cee69d628e23","tid":671404,"uid":828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T06:21:33.000Z","msg":"嗚嗚嗚"},{"pid":"d845fff906450bbe2824c03d6213f942648a289f","tid":671404,"uid":4326,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"69d30d3307d03008dc1d68fc02e2907c46981ee5","tid":671404,"uid":119900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T06:19:41.000Z","msg":"試下放左工返屋企唔出聲。會舒服啲"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T06:24:24.000Z","msg":"放工就即刻收工<br />\n<br />\n但有時屋企咁嘅環境<br />\n<br />\n又唔想返去<br />\n<br />\n我記得睇過一篇文<br />\n<br />\n大約係個男人放左工日日都起樓下唔返屋企<br />\n<br />\n依家終於睇會到<br />\n<br />\n有時一個人先係最開心最輕鬆"},{"pid":"0260444c4e863b3881c417c8eb6bbf53955c0f5e","tid":671404,"uid":79442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T06:25:06.000Z","msg":"加油 我做埋人老豆添<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"819a794067b1aa2afdf28692c3174a5420e1bb88","tid":671404,"uid":129016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T06:25:46.000Z","msg":"拍拖都咁冇得怪啦"},{"pid":"9d376bd196594c26817bf5f8420585a5aa2417c0","tid":671404,"uid":4326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"946dd53d93547c9dbce575c1e39e739fab37c63f","tid":671404,"uid":138138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T06:20:49.000Z","msg":"硬食"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T06:26:00.000Z","msg":"就像一個壓力煲遲早爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f6a51a546e7da5358aeca693d034aed4b3c21a7","tid":671404,"uid":4326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"819a794067b1aa2afdf28692c3174a5420e1bb88","tid":671404,"uid":129016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T06:25:46.000Z","msg":"拍拖都咁冇得怪啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T06:27:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唉"},{"pid":"d2fd8e23962147922cf2777840d05c3d625971ac","tid":671404,"uid":4326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0260444c4e863b3881c417c8eb6bbf53955c0f5e","tid":671404,"uid":79442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T06:25:06.000Z","msg":"加油 我做埋人老豆添<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T06:28:13.000Z","msg":"咁大壓力我驚仔都生唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc8211124e542ff2ccfe72e25a9cd36